	)
	(text "Riref	= Kiref * (Viref/Iset)\n\nKiref= 105; Viref = 0,7V; IF (LED) = 30mA\n\nRiref	= 105 * (0,7V/ 30mA)\nRiref	= 2.450 Ohm\n\nProbe:\nIset	= (Kiref*Viref)/ Riref\n		= (105*0,7V) / 2500 ohm\nIset	= 29,4 mA"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at -81.788 38.354 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "602747a1-e88f-4c94-82be-111e3f5cb90c")
	)
	(text "Die Distandzder der Leiterbahn welche nötwendig wäre\num alle 3 LED-Treiber zu verbinde ist zu umständlich\nDaher verwenden wir 2 Widerstände.\n "
